tags: I know some other people have done these but I'm here I'm queer and I have more to add
title: Some things from ii Austin
body:
• so many people around the area had lovely aesthetics and dyed hair and pride March and EVERYONE WAS SO CUTE AND POLITE AND KIND I LOVE Y'ALL, YOU’RE ALL TENS
  • WELCOME TO THE BLACK PARADE PLAYED AND WE ALL BROKE SOUND BY SCREAMING
  • Dan’s Siri threatening to beat us up if we recorded the show
  • their entrance was so cool I loved it
  • PHIL SAID YALL HOWDY AND YEEHAW AND CALLED US COWBOYS
  • “I just have all these yeehaws inside of me” - Phil (2018)
  • “Long bois” - Dan (2018)
  • On the list of things they wouldn’t do they had “erotic roleplay” and the audience LOST IT
  • Them ripping off their shirts only to reveal identical shirts on underneath
  • Dan making a list of gestures Phil wasn’t allowed to do
  • “Slide into your DMs”
  • our name was bob and we were sarcastic little shits
  • 4% of the audience stanning dapc and them shaming us for it
  • someone had a sign that said “don’t cry, craft” and it was beautiful
  • Wholesome Howell advocating to have everyone’s devices on 5% always and Evil Phil trying to make world peace bad
  • WHOLESOME HOWELL CONVINCING US THAT VOLDEMORT’S NUDES WERE A GOOD THING AND SAYING “shout out to all of us who would bang Voldemort”
  • phil’s sugar baby
  • THE LIZARD WITH THE WHISK
  • tHe SiMuLaToR
  • we sold phil’s soul to Satan and we killed dan at a furry rave
  • LADY DOOR
  • they have such adorable mannerisms, like dan nervously played with his hands the whole time and Phil would awkwardly kind of swing his left arm about and god I love them so fucking much
  • PHIL DOING THE DEEP VOICE FOR HIS EVIL PERSONA AND EVERYONE DROPPING DEAD ON THE SPOT
  • dan starting to have a crisis every two seconds and Phil going “dAN”
  • THE SUN EXPLODING
  • “The Final Countdown” playing and them coming back on stage after the first chorus
  • We sacrificed Phil whoops ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
  • Dan shooting Phil in the thigh with a slingshot and almost hitting him with the bow and arrow (he was basically aiming for phil’s crotch the whole time)
  • Dan pointing the bow at the audience and everyone screaming for him to hit them
  • The whole audience + Dan and Phil calling someone out for having their flash on
  • Phil and Dan encouraging a fan to shave their head bc they wanted to and talking about how they’ll be beautiful no matter what they do and my trichotillomanic ass SOBBING
  • PHIL TRASH #1
  • “SuPeR BeSt fRiEnDs AnD sOuLmAtEs”
  • Everyone shaking their phones during phil’s diss track
  • Phil saying “bitch” and the audience going BUCKWILD
  • DAN PLAYING THE PIANO I CRIED
  • we were all silent during the interactive introverts song and it was lovely, they’re some talented bois I LOVE THEM
  • The winning incorrect prediction was that Dan and Phil would host a live Texas rodeo while riding shrek and donkey
  • All in all it was just a wonderful night and I’m so thankful for these two dorks whom I love so much
